iv></div><div class="main_menu_list_c15b96c5448789857d052e8297e8ebea"><a title="Listen Live" aria-label="Listen Live" href="/listen-live" class class><span>Listen Live</span></a><a title="Presenters" aria-label="Presenters" href="/presenters" class class><span>Presenters</span></a><a title="Schedule" aria-label="Schedule" href="/schedule" class class><span>Schedule</span></a><a title="Contact" aria-label="Contact" href="/contact" class class><span>Contact</span></a><a title="Privacy Policy" aria-label="Privacy Policy" href="/privacy-policy" class class><span>Privacy Policy</span></a><a title="Catch Up" aria-label="Catch Up" href="/catchup" class class><span>Catch Up</span></a><a title="Slim Radio Merchandise" aria-label="Slim Radio Merchandise" href="/slim-radio-andamp-fat-belly-co" class class><span>Slim Radio Merchandise</span></a><a title="Slim TV" aria-label="Slim TV" href="/slim-tv" class class><span>Slim TV</span></a></div></div></div></div><div style="display: none;"></div></div><div class="page-head-contain__2qbow"></div><div class="page-content-contain"><div class="page-main type-page is-home layout-size-wide"><main type="main"><div class="predefined-text-home_main predefined-text"><div class="wp-block-columns"><div class="wp-block-column"><div><div class="wp-block-image is-style-default"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img src="/api/image/a7a6c499-7b57-4de4-b37a-463d6aceca16.png?g=center" alt="" class="wp-image-1009710648"/></figure></div></div><div><p class="has-text-align-center">Slim Radio is a fresh new online radio station created for the true music lover, with a vision to be the preferred radio station for West London and beyond and the first choice for quality House, Soul, Funk Disco &amp; RnB streamed worldwide. </p></div><div><p class="has-text-align-center"><strong>Our Mission to you the listener.</strong></p></div><div><p class="has-text-align-center">Slim Radio will deliver a world-class listening experience by curating the finest house, soul, and R&amp;B.</p></div><div><p class="has-text-align-center">We are connecting discerning audiences in West London and across the globe through quality sound, authentic DJs, and an unwavering passion for music.</p></div><div><p class="has-text-align-center">If you're interested in joining the Slim Radio family, please email&nbsp;<strong>join@slimradio.co.uk</strong>&nbsp;with your contact details, and a member of our team will get back to you within the next 72 hours.</p></div></div></div></div></main></div></div><div style="background-color: #000000; color: #FFFFFF; --tint: #369;" class="undefined page-footer has-#000000-background-color"><div class="page-main"><div class="wp-block-columns"><div class="wp-block-column"><img class="footer-logo__yjmqO" src="/api/image/5f3e800c-1004-44c2-b5c7-dbbc7b210d7d.png?g=center&amp;h=200" /><p>Copyright © 2026 Slim Radio</p><p><a href="https://broadrad.com/mystation">Powered by Broadcast.Radio</a></p></div><div class="wp-block-column undefined"><div class="footer-links__2yjhU footer-links"><a href="/contact">Contact</a></div></div><div class="wp-block-column social-block-col__2rT9O"><div style="flex: 1;"></div><div><h3>Find Us On:</h3><div class="social-icon-container__3QEqM"><a tabIndex="-1" class="icon-button__jPd0h" target="_blank" title="Facebook" href="https://www.facebook.com/%2F825683999981805"><svg role="img" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><title>Facebook</title><path d="M9.101 23.691v-7.98H6.627v-3.667h2.474v-1.58c0-4.085 1.848-5.978 5.858-5.978.401 0 .955.042 1.468.103a8.68 8.68 0 0 1 1.141.195v3.325a8.623 8.623 0 0 0-.653-.036 26.805 26.805 0 0 0-.733-.009c-.707 0-1.259.096-1.675.309a1.686 1.686 0 0 0-.679.622c-.258.42-.374.995-.374 1.752v1.297h3.919l-.386 2.103-.287 1.564h-3.246v8.245C19.396 23.238 24 18.179 24 12.044c0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12s-12 5.373-12 12c0 5.628 3.874 10.35 9.101 11.647Z"></path></svg></a><a tabIndex="-1" class="icon-button__jPd0h" target="_blank" title="Instagram" h